item.content:encoded:
Mathematics is one of the most complex subjects in the world. The Nobel Prize in Mathematics is awarded to those outstanding mathematics masters every year. Do you think you are good at mathematics? Math Fun Solarize is a math-related game that can test your math ability. You need to answer these math questions as soon as possible and check the scores you can get before you make a mistake. Smart kids are always good at doing math problems. If you want to exercise your calculation skills, you might as well try this game!
Mouse click or tap the screen to play.
